title: Dungeon Reset - Novel Updates

description: [The Dungeon is resetting.] Once a Dungeon has been explored and its traps were activated, it resets itself for the next ‘users’. But those resets don’t apply to me?! The only existence that has become free in the endlessly resetting dungeon. Armed with absolute grinding, Jeong Dawoon ‘the Bug’ begins his dungeon exploration!>
